It's rare part has been renovated but the front part is untouched for the sake of its legacy. You can offer 5 times namaz here. Eidain Namaz (Special Prayers offered on Festival Day) are also offered here. I request everyone to visit and explore this Masjid spend some time you will definitely find peace.
